name: startup-1
description: Aloha! Today I would like to introduce my startup website, X Grid O. Have you ever wanted to play tick tack toe but no one is available to play? Well X Grid O allows you to play tick tack toe against a program so you can hone your skills for the next time you see your friends. X Grid O is a free to play application but as it's poppularity grows, I plan to release a online multiplayer option which will cost $5 to have permanant access.
